---
title: Kebab-Inspired Lamb Burgers with Feta Potato Wedges
description: Savoury spices and grated red onion bring all the familiar flavours of grilled kebabs to these hearty lamb patties! Alongside these succulent burgers, you'll find golden potatoes gussied up with creamy feta and fresh dill.
